XCTest will use this

00:32:20.896 --> 00:32:21.856 A:middle
to detect regressions.

00:32:22.356 --> 00:32:27.906 A:middle
It will fail a test if the
new Average has increased

00:32:27.906 --> 00:32:29.746 A:middle
