00:39:13.996 --> 00:39:16.376 A:middle
But if I only want
to measure the time

00:39:16.376 --> 00:39:21.476 A:middle
of using the FileHandle, what I
might do is just move the set up

00:39:21.476 --> 00:39:23.346 A:middle
