outside of the block.

00:39:24.286 --> 00:39:25.256 A:middle
But what if I can't do that?

00:39:25.936 --> 00:39:27.456 A:middle
Sometimes, the work
that you want

00:39:27.456 --> 00:39:29.876 A:middle
to measure requires some
