00:39:56.676 --> 00:39:58.206 A:middle
You can use these to
isolate what the part

00:39:58.206 --> 00:39:58.976 A:middle
of the block you
want to measure.

00:39:59.226 --> 00:40:02.826 A:middle
You can call these once
per block invocation.


WEBVTT
